Package com.seailz.discordjv.model.guild

Record Class Member

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Record
com.seailz.discordjv.model.guild.Member
Record Components:
user - the user this guild member represents
nick - this user's guild nickname
avatar - the member's guild avatar hash //TODO: sort out avatars and images
roles - The user's roles
joinedAt - when the user joined the guild
premiumSince - when the user started boosting the guild
deaf - whether the user is deafened in voice channels
mute - whether the user is muted in voice channels
pending - whether the user has not yet passed the guild's Membership Screening requirements
permissions - total permissions of the member in the channel, including overwrites, returned when in the interaction object //TODO: sort out permissions
communicationDisabledUntil - when the user's timeout will expire and the user will be able to communicate in the guild again, null or a time in the past if the user is not timed out
All Implemented Interfaces:
Compilerable, Resolvable
public record Member(User user, String nick, String avatar, Role[] roles, String joinedAt, String premiumSince, boolean deaf, boolean mute, boolean pending, String permissions, String communicationDisabledUntil, String guildId, DiscordJv discordJv) extends Record implements Compilerable, Resolvable
Represents a member of a guild
